{"tid":180613,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★報贏不報輸？少年股神2017又來了！","createTime":"2017-03-31T04:41:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-31T10:14:33.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"174952536a37e55ee1d487cc4b7f8835f6a1447a","tid":180613,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T04:41:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">學生炒神首季獲利3成！</span><br />\n<br />\n2017年第1季投資氣氛不俗，大市上升之餘，個別股份更有亮麗表現。中大學生炒神Eric成功在首季從股票投資中獲利3成。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，今季新股和半新股表現不俗，抽中過美高域(01985)、黎氏企業(02266)，勁賺2倍！之後再炒其他半新股都有2至3成賺幅。其他股份方面，這季代表作包括捕捉到時尚環球(01520)和百奧家庭互動(02100)的升浪，賺近1倍。整體來說，今季他從股票投資上取得約3成回報。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20170331/bkn-20170331112018423-0331_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20170331%2Fbkn-20170331112018423-0331_00842_001.html&d=EyvET%2B%2BaCRTqAKFB3QLIc54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=48860f37\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20170331/bkn-20170331112018423-0331_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"0c08f867d7c22b29349921368a8dd628ba583d9f","tid":180613,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T04:42:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b27e8239cc32b219e4ac34e5843aa1216efd97c","tid":180613,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T04:42:23.000Z","msg":"d報紙成日loop呢d題材唔厭既咩？"},{"pid":"2999beab5fd393389a80e349140f2f81a5077fd3","tid":180613,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T04:42:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>d報紙成日loop呢d題材唔厭既咩？</blockquote><br />\n次次報撚完都見頂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f486db14c32d600f1d1ddc9f71573a3b41e5d511","tid":180613,"uid"